Reasoning: The paper deals with graphical models with latent variables and proposes a sequence of relaxations to constrain hidden variable models. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as Information Theory (cs.IT) which deals with the study of communication systems and their properties, Machine Learning (cs.LG) which deals with the development of algorithms that can learn from data, Social and Information Networks (cs.SI) which deals with the analysis of social networks and their properties, Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) which deals with the study of algorithms and data structures, and Systems and Control (cs.SY) which deals with the analysis and control of complex systems.
